        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[🤧#擤鼻涕方法不对可能会造成炎症# 一降温，就能听到身边此起彼伏的咳嗽和擤鼻涕声[允悲] 而鼻涕擤不对，可能会引发中耳、眼睛相关的炎症[吃惊] 正确擤鼻涕方...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[🤧<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%93%A4%E9%BC%BB%E6%B6%95%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%B9%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%82%8E%E7%97%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%93%A4%E9%BC%BB%E6%B6%95%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%AF%B9%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%82%8E%E7%97%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#擤鼻涕方法不对可能会造成炎症#</span></a> 一降温，就能听到身边此起彼伏的咳嗽和擤鼻涕声<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[允悲]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yunbei-a14a649db8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 而鼻涕擤不对，可能会引发中耳、眼睛相关的炎症<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 正确擤鼻涕方法快看👇🏻<br><br>✅上身向前倾斜，这个姿势有利于排出鼻窦内的分泌物；<br><br>✅用手指压住一侧鼻孔，擤另一侧鼻孔的鼻涕，同时擤两个鼻孔的鼻涕容易增加鼻内气压，增加发生中耳炎的概率；<br><br>✅擤鼻涕时不能特别用力。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（健康中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkywnaweeog20fk08qgy8.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 19 Dec 2023 02:50:05 GMT</pubDate>
