            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>骨头汤真的能补钙吗？<br><br>并不能！🙅🏻<br><br>骨头的钙含量很高，但是非常难溶解，吸收就更难了。检测结果显示，1公斤排骨熬成的骨头汤中，钙含量只有15毫克，不及骨头中的万分之一......<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[允悲]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yunbei-a14a649db8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 至于骨髓和骨油，其实是脂肪含量居多，吃多了还容易长胖。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（科普中国） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hky2guhs75g20gk09b4qp.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
